{"word":"G4039 - περιοικέω - perioikéō - per-ee-oy-keh'-o - Dwell round about","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιοικέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">perioikéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-oy-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dwell round about</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுற்றிவாசமாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to dwell round about"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G3611 - οἰκέω - oikéō - oy-keh'-o/3611\">G3611</a>; to <i>reside around</i>, that is, <i>be</i> a <i>neighbor:</i> - dwell round about.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}